the CSS code:
.header-class {
    background-color: antiquewhite;
    text-align: center;
}

.nav {
    background-color: blanchedalmond;
    line-height: 20px;
}

.menu-items {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: large;
}

.table th {
    border: 5px solid brown;
}

.table {
    width: 100%;
    border-spacing: 50px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.F {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: burlywood;
}



